                        </details>
                    </figure>

                    <figure>
                        <img src="/images/line_graph_1990.png" alt="Indicators line graph from 1990 to 2026">
                        <figcaption>Figure 3. Normalized trends of VIX, Gold and Oil Prices (1990-2026)</figcaption>
                        <details style="margin-top: 10px; text-align: left; cursor: pointer;">
                            <summary style="font-weight: bold; color: var(--link-color);">Show Code</summary>
                            <pre
                                style="background: #f4f4f4; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; overflow-x: auto; font-size: 0.85rem; text-align: left; cursor: auto; margin-top: 10px;"><code># Normalize df_1990 for plotting
